Market News April 23, 2018 / 10:35 AM / Updated 14 minutes ago BRIEF-Henry Schein - As Part Of Deal With Vets First & Before Closing, Co Expects To Buy Minority Interest In U.S. Animal Health Business For About $365 Million Reuters Staff 1 Min Read

* HENRY SCHEIN - AS PART OF DEAL WITH VETS FIRST & BEFORE CLOSING, CO EXPECTS TO BUY MINORITY INTEREST IN U.S. ANIMAL HEALTH BUSINESS FOR ABOUT $365 MILLION Source text: ( bit.ly/2HRYdsf ) Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
